The room features beige carpeting, cream-colored walls with crown molding, and a large wall-to-wall mirror that reflects the equipment and the room's layout. Visible equipment includes a Cybex leg press machine, a weight bench with brown padding, an elliptical trainer, a stationary bike, and a rack of dumbbells. There is a white door on the left with a small white sign taped to it, and a wooden door visible in the reflection. A television is mounted on the wall in the background, visible through the mirror.
